            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              <strong>Enterprise Agreement:</strong> If you are using Ralph on behalf of an organization, you represent that you have the authority to bind that organization to these Terms, and "you" refers to both you individually and the organization.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              <strong>Minimum Age:</strong> You must be at least 18 years old to use Ralph. The service is designed for professional use by qualified investment professionals.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-neutral-700">2. Service Description</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Ralph is an enterprise software solution that:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside space-y-2 ml-6 text-secondary">
              <li>Deploys on your own infrastructure (self-hosted or private cloud)</li>
              <li>Provides AI-powered tools for portfolio management and reporting</li>
              <li>Operates without accessing or storing your data on our systems</li>
              <li>Integrates with your existing systems and security protocols</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-neutral-700">3. License and Usage Rights</h2>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary mb-2 mt-6">3.1 License Grant</h3>
