              If Ralph fails to meet these warranties, we will use commercially reasonable efforts to correct the issue or provide a workaround.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary mb-2 mt-6">9.2 Professional Services Warranty</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We warrant that our professional services (deployment, training, consulting) will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary mb-2 mt-6">9.3 Warranty Disclaimers</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              <strong>The above warranties are exclusive and in lieu of all other warranties.</strong> To the extent permitted by law, we disclaim all other warranties, express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.
