            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We do not warrant that Ralph will be error-free or that its use will be uninterrupted, as system performance depends on your infrastructure and configuration.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-neutral-700">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary mb-2 mt-6">10.1 Liability Cap</h3>
