              <strong>TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, OUR TOTAL LIABILITY FOR ALL CLAIMS ARISING FROM OR RELATED TO THESE TERMS OR RALPH SHALL NOT EXCEED THE GREATER OF:</strong>
            </p>
