              <li>$100,000 USD; OR</li>
              <li>The total fees paid by you for Ralph in the twelve (12) months immediately preceding the event giving rise to the claim</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary mb-2 mt-6">10.2 Excluded Damages</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              <strong>IN NO EVENT SHALL WE BE LIABLE FOR:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside space-y-2 ml-6 text-secondary mb-4">
