          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-neutral-700">17. Entire Agreement and Modifications</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              These Terms, together with the following documents (if applicable), constitute the entire agreement between you and Beneficious regarding Ralph:
            </p>
